==Swedish==
===Etymology===
From [[tyngd]] (''[[weight]]'') + [[-lös#Swedish|-lös]] (''[[-less]]'') + [[-het#Swedish|-het]] (''[[-ness]]'')

===Noun===
'''tyngdlöshet'''

#[[weightlessness|Weightlessness]]; the state of being in a [[zero g]] environment; not sensing any pull of [[gravtiy]].

